OL,3,CFather 'grateful' to donors two years
OL,4,Con from his son's life-saving surgery
OL,6,FThe toddler was fitted with a Berlin
OL,7,FHeart to keep him alive while he
OL,8,Fwaited for a transplant at Great
OL,9,FOrmond Street Hospital. A donor heart
OL,10,Fbecame available shortly after Laurie
OL,11,Fcelebrated his first birthday,
OL,12,Fresulting in nine hours of surgery.
OL,14,FNow nearly three years old, Laurie is
OL,15,F'loving life' with his two brothers,
OL,16,FOsian and Kit. His dad, Tom, said: "We
OL,17,Fare eternally grateful to Laurie's
OL,18,Fdonor family and that they said yes to
OL,19,Forgan donation during an unimaginably
OL,20,Fdifficult time. We think of them every
OL,21,Fday."
